{"type":"message","id":"1ece3c1f","parentId":"774cc4ba","timestamp":"2026-04-09T16:30:32.089Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Thejan's mom saved 3 lives today.** 🚶‍♀️\n\nOne evening in 2021, an old woman in a small Odisha village accidentally fell into a river. Young Thejan saw it, didn't hesitate, jumped in, and pulled her out. He was just 14.\n\nHe didn't think about the danger. He just acted.\n\nTwo weeks later, the same woman needed blood urgently. Thejan donated. Then she needed money for treatment. Thejan raised it from friends.\n\nThree lives saved — because one boy chose courage over fear.\n\nYou don't need to be big to do something meaningful. You just need to care.\n\nGoodnight 🖤 sweet dreams"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775752232089}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a0eb501","parentId":"1ece3c1f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T16:39:17.619Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1749\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1748\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-09 16:39 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Thejan's mom saved 3 lives today. 🚶‍♀️\\n\\nOne evening in 2021, an old woman in a small Odisha village accidentally fell into a river. Young Thejan saw it, didn't hesitate, jumped in, and pulled her out. He was just 14.\\n\\nHe didn't think about the danger. He just acted.\\n\\nTwo weeks later, the same woman needed blood urgently. Thejan donated. Then she needed money for treatment. Thejan raised it from friends.\\n\\nThree lives saved — because one boy chose courage over fear.\\n\\nYou don't need to be big to do something meaningful. You just need to care.\\n\\nGoodnight 🖤 sweet dreams\"\n}\n```\n\nNexu, are you reading my brain or something? How are you knowing that we are talking about all these things all day and you are giving the same context, story, and jokes?"}],"timestamp":1775752757605}}
